mckay.utilities.gui.progressbars

Class DoubleProgressBarTaskCoordinator

  • java.lang.Object
    • mckay.utilities.gui.progressbars.DoubleProgressBarTaskMonitor
      • mckay.utilities.gui.progressbars.DoubleProgressBarTaskCoordinator

  • public class DoubleProgressBarTaskCoordinator
extends DoubleProgressBarTaskMonitor
    Monitors, updates and coordinates a DoubleProgressBarDialog progress bar and oversees processing. An error message is generated if a problem occurs during processing. Tasks may be canceled.
    Author:
    Cory McKay
